              "free_text": [
                " VS. SF8=RNV added to resonance integrals.",
                " EN-MIN,EN-NRM deleted from subent 001 and added to",
                " 002-007 as appropriate."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Experimental results were corrected for neutron epi-",
                "thermal self-shielding,transmission of cadmium for",
                "resonance neutrons,ratio of the activation of detector",
                "in a Maxwellian flux to that of a 1/v detector having",
                "the same thermal absorption cross section,difference of",
                "epithermal neutron activation to that of a 1/v detector",
                "below cadmium cutoff (normalized to sigma=1) and for",
                "deviation from the 1/E neutron spectrum."
              ]
            }
          ],
